The invention relates to a weighing device of a dump truck, comprising a sensor combination and a weighing instrument. The sensor combination is arranged between the lower part of a carriage and a truck beam, and the weighing instrument arranged on a truck head is used for receiving a sensor combination signal; the sensor combination includes an axle pin sensor arranged at the tail part of the beam of the dump truck and a pressure sensor which is arranged on the beam of the dump truck and is connected with an oil outlet pipeline communicated with a hydraulic supporting rod; the axle pin sensor is used for transmitting a weighing signal to the weighing instrument by an axle pin sensor signal transmission wire which is arranged on a truck body and is connected with the axle pin sensor; and the pressure sensor is used for transmitting the weighing signal to the weighing instrument by a pressure sensor signal transmission wire which is arranged on the truck body and is connected with the pressure sensor. The weighing device solves the technical problems that the weighing device can timely as well as conveniently weigh the loading quantity of the truck and can measure the weight of loaded goods at the same time as the goods are unloaded due to adopting the dynamic weighing mode.
