The invention is applicable to an automatic weighing technology of cargo loaded in a cargotank of a self-discharging car which uses a hydraulic pump to push a support rod to further push the cargotank to be discharged, relating to a weighing method of a dynamic self-discharging car scales. The method comprises the following steps: valid weighing data by a shaft pin sensor arranged at the self-discharging car beam tail and valid weighing data by a pressure sensor connected with an oil outlet pipeline which is communicated with the hydraulic pressure support rod and is arranged at the self-discharging car beam are obtained; when calibration weight is put in one point randomly on an empty car, weight math equation is carried out on the valid weighing data by the shaft pin sensor and the valid weighing data by the hydraulic sensor to obtain weighing coefficient, thus solving the technical problem of the method that the self-discharging car can weigh the weight of the loaded cargo while loading, driving and discharging.
